 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath11k/hw.c   |   4 +-
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath11k/mac.c  | 119 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 3 files changed, 122 insertions(+), 2 deletions(-)

